<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #0066cc;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        strong {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        a {
            color: #0066cc;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            background: #f8f8f8;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <p>Dear <%=name%></p>
        <p>Your account has been successfully created for  <%=appName%>. Here are your login credentials:</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%=email%></p>
        <p><strong>Password:</strong> <%=generatePassword%></p>
        <p>Please use the provided credentials to <a href=<%=appLink%> target="_blank">log in to your account</a>.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to contact us.</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing <%=appName%> !</p>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>Best regards,<br>
            Eurobose </p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>